# Force LF line endings on checkout regardless of the host's
# core.autocrlf setting. The emscripten build's generated .js shim
# must stay LF or the designer's bundler diffs it against an old
# wasm/.js pair on Windows.
* text=auto eol=lf

# The generated WASM + glue artifacts are committed under public/
# for the designer's copy-wasm.sh to pick up. Treat as binary.
public/jlp_wasm.wasm binary
public/jlp_wasm.js  -text -diff
